<div id="instructions">
  <h2>Instructions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Select 'Easy', 'Medium' or 'Tricky' to make a new rule.</li>
  <li>Enter an input number and leave the output number blank, then press 'Calculate' to see what output
  number the rule gives. Press 'Record' to keep the result to refer to
  later. Keep doing this until you think you know what
  the rule is.</li>
  <li>Enter a new input number <em>and</em> the output number you
  think the rule will generate, then press 'Check'. You must do this
  twice in a row to win.</li>
  </ol>
  <p>Note that a rule can be written in different ways. You might have
  written the rule differently than the computer, but still be
  right.</p>
</div>
